\par\plain {\f2\fs22\b0\i0 Durathror smiled, twirled his moustache again. "There are many exercises you could be doing, but if you are doing all the ones we taught nalini, then that is more than enough. You do not want to over train, that tires you and drains you. If an exercise is not working, then it should be changed. You appear to be progressing satisfactorily though. But if you like, one evening I will run you through some tests."}
