\par\plain {\f2\fs22\b0\i0 "It doesn't shock me" liz replied. "It's just that I was brought up to be a virgin when I married...." suddenly she looked sad. "At least the nuns did. My parents said it didn't really matter, us black fellas don't see it as important as the white fellas do..." She was reverting to dialect again, indicating she was nervous. She put her right hand to her mouth, began chewing the knuckle.}
