\par\plain {\f2\fs22\b0\i0 "And you'll learn that too liz..." "..and one day you and your partner will be able to..." "..make noises like that!" nalini finished laughing.}
\par\plain {\f2\fs22\b0\i0 Liz smiled, a happy sincere smile. "It's okay, I'm over my past. Occasionally it upsets me when I think about it. These days I don't have sex because I don't have a boyfriend, and I don't have a boyfriend because I haven't found one I like enough."}
